overview: A kindly, elderly couple who run a New York City boarding house form the steady center around which the lives and loves of their various residents unfold. Borrowed money, a lovelorn chorus girl, and a tragic misunderstanding set in motion the chain of events in East of Fifth Avenueâ€™s tender pageant of life.
tagline: The GRAND HOTEL of a New York boarding house!
title: East of Fifth Avenue
